@page "/"

<PageTitle>MBOX to PST Converter</PageTitle>

<h1>MBOX to PST Email Converter</h1>

<p class="lead">
    A .NET application for converting email files between MBOX and PST formats with bidirectional support.
</p>

<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-header">
                <h5>Features</h5>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Bidirectional conversion</strong> between MBOX and PST formats</li>
                    <li><strong>Gmail integration</strong> with OAuth2 authentication</li>
                    <li>Email viewing and preview capabilities</li>
                    <li>Interactive file path selection</li>
                    <li>Real-time conversion progress display</li>
                    <li>Preserves email metadata, attachments, and formatting</li>
                    <li>Error handling and validation</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-header">
                <h5>Supported Conversions</h5>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
                <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-3">
                    <span class="badge bg-primary me-2">.mbox</span>
                    <span class="bi bi-arrow-right mx-2"></span>
                    <span class="badge bg-success">.pst</span>
                </div>
                <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                    <span class="badge bg-success me-2">.pst</span>
                    <span class="bi bi-arrow-right mx-2"></span>
                    <span class="badge bg-primary">.mbox</span>
                </div>
                <hr />
                <p class="small text-muted">
                    The conversion direction is automatically determined by the input and output file extensions.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="row mt-4">
    <div class="col-12">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-header">
                <h5>Getting Started</h5>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
                <ol>
                    <li>Navigate to the <a href="/converter" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-primary">Email Converter</a> page</li>
                    <li>Enter the path to your input file (.mbox or .pst format)</li>
                    <li>Enter the desired output file path with the target extension</li>
                    <li>Click "Load Emails" to preview the emails in the input file</li>
                    <li>Click "Convert" to start the conversion process</li>
                    <li>Monitor the progress and wait for completion</li>
                </ol>
                
                <h6 class="mt-3">Gmail Integration:</h6>
                <ol>
                    <li>Navigate to the <a href="/mailbox" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-success">Mailbox</a> page</li>
                    <li>Click on the "Gmail" tab</li>
                    <li>Click "Connect Gmail" to authenticate with your Google account</li>
                    <li>Use "Refresh Emails" to fetch your latest Gmail messages</li>
                    <li>Enable auto-refresh for periodic updates</li>
                    <li>Optionally save Gmail messages to MBOX format</li>
                </ol>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
